{"tid":1942103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警世」如果你真係想贏，請停止批鬥自己人，好似龍門，肥蛙同小車手呢啲咁","createTime":"2020-03-25T00:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T01:15:37.000Z","uid":28435,"like":30,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"74b94fa44b377e11a2d06992e60b81d17a87e83a","tid":1942103,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:30:30.000Z","msg":"你話佢地係偽黃借黃色經濟圈食人血饅頭，但佢地全部係今次抗暴事件都係唔同程度唔同方面出心出力，付出既程度可能唔同，但大家都係為香港好<br />\n<br />\n唔通背負暴動罪/襲警罪既手足，又可以批鬥你地無案底安坐家中打國際戰線既手足唔夠黃嗎，所以請不要批鬥指責同路人，不要令我們黃圈愈批鬥愈縮 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n而且你話佢地借抗爭搵錢，要知道黃色經濟圈就係用錢嚟推動，你做唔起搵唔到食邊個加入黃圈壯大我地陣營，要記住我地係黃色經濟圈，唔係黃色蝕本圈 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FAKY7L8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFAKY7L8.png&h=57e0996a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44ca95ddcfc9534e179e8b768f010ef5eb888080","tid":1942103,"uid":7484,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:31:43.000Z","msg":"其實主要係五毛係到分化"},{"pid":"6df1568522bb52c05cb7f92ed2fcd3b6766116c0","tid":1942103,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5b9d6ad75b68aff565609fa5c668359e7a8b67","tid":1942103,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:32:50.000Z","msg":"諗落有道理，推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf20bb799538dfe5f55fd5c5c4a7ccc3f66019f","tid":1942103,"uid":82532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:35:03.000Z","msg":"抄人嘢喎唔係咩"},{"pid":"82e054a82dc3417714f3769b8b28f912c93cff48","tid":1942103,"uid":335434,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyT